        "⚽ *BTTS leaders (last 8 games)*\n"
        f"{btts_lines}\n\n"
        "🔒 *Clean sheet leaders (last 8 games)*\n"
        f"{cs_lines}"
        f"{FOOTER.format(version=version)}"
